    dc:description "FIGURE 45. Gammarus alius, sp. nov., from left side, male, 15.0 mm, paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/281125/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281126>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46 – 53. Gammarus alius, sp. nov., male, 16.0 mm, holotype: (46) head; (47) antenna 1; (48) antenna 2, lateral view; (49) antenna 2, lateral view, inner face, in part; (50) urosome; (51) mandible, left; (52) mandible, right; (53) mandibular palp. Scale bars 0.2 mm, if not indicated otherwise." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/281126/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281132>
    dc:description "FIGURES 81 – 85. Gammarus alius, sp. nov., male, 16.0 mm, holotype: (81) flagellum of antenna 2, ventral view, in part; (82) the same enlarged; (83) flagellum of antenna 2, lateral view, in part; (84) pleopod 1, ventral view, in part; (85) pleopod 1, lateral view, in part. Scale bars 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/281132/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281128>
    dc:description "FIGURES 63 – 66. Gammarus alius, sp. nov., male, 16.0 mm, holotype: (63) gnathopod 1; (64) propodus of gnathopod 1; (65) gnathopod 2; (66) propodus of gnathopod 2. Scale bars 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/281128/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281127>
    dc:description "FIGURES 54 – 62. Gammarus alius, sp. nov., male, 16.0 mm, holotype: (54) maxilla 2; (55) maxilla 1, left; (56) inosculate setae of maxilla 1 inner plate; (57) palp of maxilla 1, right; (58) upper lip; (59) lower lip; (60) maxilliped; (61) outer plate of maxilliped; (62) inner plate of maxilliped. Scale bars 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/281127/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281133>
    dc:description "FIGURES 86 – 89. Different conditions of upper lip of Gammarus alius, sp. nov., male, 15.0 mm: (86) dorsal view (with visible adjoining sclerite); male, 16.0 mm, holotype: (87) dorsal view; (88) ventral view; male, 15.0 mm: (89) hook damaged owing to careless preparation, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/281133/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281129>
    dc:description "FIGURES 67 – 74. Gammarus alius, sp. nov., male, 16.0 mm, holotype: (67) pereopod 3; (68) pereopod 4; (69) pleopod 3; (70) uropod 1; (71) uropod 2; (72) uropod 3; (73) terminal article of uropod 3; (74) telson. Scale bars 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/281129/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281130>
    dc:description "FIGURES 75 – 77. Gammarus alius, sp. nov., male, 16.0 mm, holotype: (75) pereopod 5; (76) pereopod 6; (77) pereopod 7. Scale bars 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/281130/files/figure.png" ;
