<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281131>
    dc:description "FIGURES 78 – 80. Gammarus alius, sp. nov., male, 16.0 mm, holotype: (78) epimera 1 – 3; (79) pleopod 1; (80) pleopod 2. Scale bars 0.2 mm." ;
